        </item>
        <item>
            <title>調位事件苦主回港後收到 HK Express 道歉　「但快運仍未就事件作合理解釋」</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/07/22/hkexpress-apology-to-chengs-but-still-no-full-explanation/life-tech/travel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=hkexpress-apology-to-chengs-but-still-no-full-explanation</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/07/22/hkexpress-apology-to-chengs-but-still-no-full-explanation/life-tech/travel/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Ngan Ivan]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 08:00:30 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[城中熱話]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[旅遊]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Hk Express]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[香港快運]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1251783</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">最近航空公司香港快運（HK Express）的強行調位事件引起熱議，事緣有兩名家長連同兩名子女在香港快運前往日本的航班上，強行要求已付費揀位的乘客讓出座位，而航空公司僅是向被搶座位乘客表示可以回港後申請退款，處理手法令一眾網民不滿。事件的最新消息為被搶座位的鄭氏夫婦回港後已得到香港快運聯絡致歉，但表示仍未得到事件的有關合理解釋。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1251787 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/unwire-1721626780-694x544.jpg" alt="HK Express" width="694" height="544" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/unwire-1721626780-694x544.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/unwire-1721626780.jpg 1147w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">圖片來源：<a href="https://www.facebook.com/photo/?fbid=10160062787418144&amp;set=g.638762621229829">HK Express 香港快運及旅行資訊關注組</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">香港快運事後作出的回應，指該一家四口最初預訂的座位因機型不同的關係變成了緊急出口座位排，而其中兩名乘客因未成年不能坐在緊急出口座位排，與另一排四名乘客（包括已付費揀位的兩位乘客）的協商後安排調位。然而鄭氏夫婦表示從頭到尾都沒有與他們協商過就被強行調位，直指香港快運講大話。香港快運在鄭氏夫婦回港後立即進行聯絡並致歉，指早前與員工的溝通不足，導致作出了不實的回應。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">鄭氏夫婦得到了快運的道歉後，表示目前快運仍然未有就事件作出合理的解釋，希望快運可以盡快展開調查，要求快運作正式的書面道歉並向公眾交代事件的合理解釋。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">資料來源：<a href="https://finance.mingpao.com/fin/instantf/20240722/1721613308139/hk-express%e7%88%ad%e4%bd%8d-%e7%95%b6%e4%ba%8b%e4%ba%ba%e9%84%ad%e6%b0%8f-%e5%9b%9e%e6%b8%af%e5%be%8c%e5%b7%b2%e7%8d%b2%e5%bf%ab%e9%81%8b%e8%81%af%e7%b5%a1%e8%87%b4%e6%ad%89-%e6%83%9f%e5%85%ac%e5%8f%b8%e4%bb%8d%e6%9c%aa%e6%9c%89%e5%90%88%e7%90%86%e8%a7%a3%e9%87%8b?fbclid=IwZXh0bgNhZW0CMTAAAR2NvUGY0PXZKK2vVcrspHc5NoHX4SHvK8U-03BLf_gRsI1vq9WUcHcZb8c_aem_b9mLYcu8t2Ab9MQn3f7sjw">明報</a></p><p>圖片來源：<a href="https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1670182-20221008.htm">RTHK</a></p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/08/hk-express-2/life-tech/travel/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">HK Express 新 4 級行李制改逐件計　網民：加錢都解決不了問題</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/22/hkexpress-apology-to-chengs-but-still-no-full-explanation/life-tech/travel/">調位事件苦主回港後收到 HK Express 道歉　「但快運仍未就事件作合理解釋」</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2024/07/22/hkexpress-apology-to-chengs-but-still-no-full-explanation/life-tech/travel/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
            <slash:comments>0</slash:comments>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title>ZEEKR 009 最豪 MPV 右軚版登場　首創健康減壓模式 + 大量內外高科技元素</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/07/22/zeekr-009-2/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=zeekr-009-2</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/07/22/zeekr-009-2/life-tech/auto/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 08:00:24 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[汽車科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Zeekr]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Zeekr 009]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[純電動車]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1250814</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>ZEEKR 早前宣佈正式登陸香港，今日公佈豪華旗艦 MPV 全新 ZEEKR 009，其左軚和右軚版本全球同步發售。 香港一換一補貼售價為 $750,000 起。 即日起正式公開接受預訂。ZEEKR CEO 在發布會上表示，今年 6 月 ZEEKR 品牌單月交付首度突破 20,000 台；今年上半年，ZEEKR 品牌累計交付超過 87,800 台，在售價 20 萬元以上中國純電品牌中排名第一。 </p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1251789" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/allnew009exterior1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/allnew009exterior1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/allnew009exterior1-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>ZEEKR 009 豪華 MPV 車身採用流線型設計，搭配精緻的前後燈組，整體造型富有現代感。全系共有 5 種外觀顏色，3 種輪圈造型供用戶選擇，滿足不同用戶的個性需求。ZEEKR 009 全系升級搭載高性能碳化矽電驅系統，雙摩打四驅版本馬力達 603 匹，0-100km/h 加速僅需 4.6 秒，比肩高性超跑。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1251793" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/allnew009exterior4-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/allnew009exterior4-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/allnew009exterior4-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1251829" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/4-11-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/4-11-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/4-11.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1251800" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/lifestyle24-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/lifestyle24-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/lifestyle24-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1251790" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/allnew009exterior2-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/allnew009exterior2-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/allnew009exterior2-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲車身採用流線型設計</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1251815" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/launcheventpics4-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/launcheventpics4-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/launcheventpics4-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲全系共有 5 種外觀顏色，3 種輪圈造型供用戶選擇</p><p>先從內籠設計講起，全新 ZEEKR 009 提供 4 種內飾風格，座椅採用 NAPPA 頭層真皮和夢幻回彈海綿，座椅整體寬度達到 0.7 米，支援最多 16 項調節，頭枕音響、加熱、通風和按摩等功能應有盡有。後排座椅更配備了 Eames Chair 模式，靠背可調至 132 度，坐墊前部可升高 20 毫米，腿託可抬升至 90 度，與前排座椅背後的腳踏組成完整平面，能完全伸展雙腳，緩解旅途疲勞。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1251814" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/shootingtitbits15-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/shootingtitbits15-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/shootingtitbits15-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲頭枕設有音響</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1251812" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/shootingtitbits18-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/shootingtitbits18-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/shootingtitbits18-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲座椅採用夢幻回彈海綿，支援最多 16 項調節</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1251794" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/20240722134514-694x464.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="464" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/20240722134514-694x464.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/20240722134514.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲後排座椅配備 Eames Chair 模式</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1251795" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/20240722134456-694x464.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="464" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/20240722134456-694x464.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/20240722134456.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1251796" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/20240722134548-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/20240722134548-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/20240722134548.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲座椅採用 NAPPA 頭層真皮</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1251799" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/lifestyle23-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/lifestyle23-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/lifestyle23-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲靠背可調至 132 度，坐墊前部可升高 20 毫米，腿託可抬升至 90 度</p><p>中控台和娛樂系統方面，前排配備了 15 吋中控大螢幕，後排則配備了 17 吋娛樂大螢幕，皆採用最新 iPad Pro 同款雙層 OLED 屏幕。另設有恆溫冰箱，製冷最低零下 6°C，制熱最高 50°C，支援 24 小時離車工作，並同時亦可用手機 App 控制，還帶有紫外線殺菌功能，可放心保存藥品和嬰兒食品。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1251816" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/lifestyle22-1-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/lifestyle22-1-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/lifestyle22-1-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲前排配備了 15 吋中控大螢幕，採用 iPad Pro 同款雙層 OLED 螢幕</p><p>ZEEKR 009 配備多種高科技系統，全系標準配置兩顆完全獨立的 8295 座艙晶元，據廠商稱能夠滿足至少未來 5 年的座艙算力需求，保護整車隱私安全。ZEEKR 009 亦加入了 KR AI 大模型，將 ZEEKR 智能語音助手 EVA 全面升級為 AI EVA，例如進入隧道時會主動建議關閉車窗打開內迴圈，回家停車時會基於通勤習慣提前預測第二天的電量，並主動提醒及時充電。ZEEKR 009 系統內置 ZEEKR 「極拓 APP」，可下載只能在手機上使用的應用程式。 ZEEKR 09 亦預裝騰訊會議 Rooms，為商務用家提供方便安全的視像會議體驗。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1251825 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/6-8-694x520.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="520" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/6-8-694x520.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/6-8-scaled.jpg 1201w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1251826" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/1-35-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/1-35-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/1-35.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1251827" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/2-20-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/2-20-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/2-20.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1251828" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/3-14-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/3-14-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/3-14.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1251804" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/lifestyle28-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/lifestyle28-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/lifestyle28-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"> </p><p>行車安全系統方面，全新 ZEEKR 009 擁有全方位安全警報系統，以及守護用戶隱私的極致安全。ZEEKR 009 的汽車安全資料庫通過最嚴苛的測試驗證安全，規模是行業平均水準的 5 倍。ZEEKR 009 配備前雙搖臂 + 後集成式多連桿的獨立懸掛，全系標準配備 CCD 電磁減振，並升級了雙腔空氣懸架。ZEEKR 009 滿足「母嬰級」使用標準，同時通過了中汽中心兒童綠色座艙認證以及中環聯合認證中心生態紡織品認證。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1251806" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/lifestyle211-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/lifestyle211-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/lifestyle211-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1251818" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/shootingtitbits33-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/shootingtitbits33-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/shootingtitbits33-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>ZEEKR 009 標配 ZEEKR 首創的「健康減壓艙」功能，在「休憩」和「治癒」模式之外，首次推出「冥想模式」，內置 8 套不同場景的冥想課程，智能聯動音樂、燈光、螢幕和座椅振子，讓乘客進入身心放鬆的境界。 此外亦加入了「足底養生」，在第二排座椅的腳踏上，加入了可獨立控制的足底加熱功能，溫度 3 檔可調。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1251823" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/20240722141950-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/20240722141950-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/20240722141950.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲第二排座椅的腳踏上加入可獨立控制的足底加熱功能</p><h2>規格（<strong><b> </b></strong>6 座行政版及 7 座中通道版）</h2><table><tbody><tr><td width="185"><p><strong><b>摩打類別</b></strong><strong><b> </b></strong></p></td><td width="447"><p>高性能永磁同步電驅動系統：雙電機</p></td></tr><tr><td width="185"><p><strong><b>電池容量</b></strong></p></td><td width="447"><p>116 kWh</p></td></tr><tr><td width="185"><p><strong><b>最大馬力</b></strong></p></td><td width="447"><p>603hp </p></td></tr><tr><td width="185"><p><strong><b>最大扭力</b></strong></p></td><td width="447"><p>693 Nm</p></td></tr><tr><td width="185"><p><strong><b>0–100 km/h</b></strong></p></td><td width="447"><p>4.6 s</p></td></tr><tr><td width="185"><p><strong><b>續航力</b></strong><strong><b> （WLTP）</b></strong></p></td><td width="447"><p>580 km</p></td></tr><tr><td width="185"><p><strong><b>最大充電功率</b></strong></p></td><td width="447"><p>150 kW （DC）</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong><b>香港一換一補貼售價</b></strong></p></td><td><p>港幣 $750,000 起</p></td></tr></tbody></table><p>ZEEKR Space：<br />地址： 香港灣仔告士打道 39 號夏愨大廈地下 A 舖<br />服務時間： 星期一至日及公眾假期，上午 9 時正至晚上 8 時正</p><p>ZEEKR Gallery：<br />地址： 香港太古城太古灣道 12 號地下<br />服務時間： 星期一至日及公眾假期，上午 9 時正至晚上 8 時正</p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/18/zeekr-x/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">ZEEKR X 右軚版本登場，四驅版馬力達 428 匹</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/17/%e6%a5%b5%e6%b0%aa-zeekr-x-%e9%a6%99%e6%b8%af%e8%a9%a6%e9%a7%95-b-%e6%9f%b1%e5%89%b5%e6%84%8f%e7%a7%91%e6%8a%80%e5%af%b5%e7%89%a9%e8%bb%8a%e4%b8%bb%e6%9c%80%e6%84%9b/unwire_podcast/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">極氪 Zeekr X 香港試駕 : B 柱創意科技寵物車主最愛</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/08/zeekr-x-rhd-hong-kong-macau/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Zeekr X 右軚版本投產，香港澳門或成全球首發市場</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/22/zeekr-009-2/life-tech/auto/">ZEEKR 009 最豪 MPV 右軚版登場　首創健康減壓模式 + 大量內外高科技元素</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
